post.title: L IS REAL 2401 has finally been fulfilled: 24 years and 1 month after the release of Super Mario 64, the source code for N64 games was leaked revealing Luigi, beta stages, and original studio quality sound files

body:
>She pointed out that the numbers from "L is real 2401", if separated, could mean 24 years and 1 month, which is when the leak was discovered. She also stated that if the numbers were added up individually they would equal 7, which is the number associated with the month July. And lastly, if the numbers 24 and 01 were added together they equal 25, which is the day Luigi was found inside the game's source code.

Mother of god... It was real all along. L  WAS REAL ALL ALONG!
body_html:
She pointed out that the numbers from "L is real 2401", if separated, could mean 24 years and 1 month, which is when the leak was discovered. She also stated that if the numbers were added up individually they would equal 7, which is the number associated with the month July. And lastly, if the numbers 24 and 01 were added together they equal 25, which is the day Luigi was found inside the game's source code.

Mother of god... It was real all along. L WAS REAL ALL ALONG!
